Package de.uni_stuttgart.ims.nlpbase.nlp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    POSUtils
    Wrapper around Parts of Speech as assigned by tagger or parser to ensure easy adaptability to a new tagest or language.
    Sentence
    Encapsulates a sentence as a sequence of words and a dependency structure.
    SRLSentence
    Extends a sentence to contain Semantic Role Labeling information.
    Word
    Represents all information about one word in a sentence: id, form, lemma, POS, deprel, head id, children, ...
  • Enum Summary

    Different groupings / annotations for arguments.
    POSUtils.POSCategory
    category according to universal tagset (Petrov et al.
    PredicateDirection
    Direction of a comparison (E1 is inferior/superior to E2 + undefined).
    PredicateType
    Comparison type ranked, superlative, equative, difference, undefined;
